S

setBorrowerId(int) - Method in class Book
Sets the given id as the id of the current borrower of this book, -1 if no patron is currently borrowing it.
stringRepresentation() - Method in class Book
Returns a string representation of the book, which is a sequence of the title, author, year of publication and the total literary value of the book, separated by commas, enclosed in square brackets.
stringRepresentation() - Method in class Patron
Returns a string representation of the patron, which is a sequence of its first and last name, separated by a single white space.
suggestBookToPatron(int) - Method in class Library
Suggest the patron with the given id the book he will enjoy the most, out of all available books he will enjoy, if any such exist.
